{
  "id": "2021-11-18_screen_english",
  "date": "2021-11-18",
  "corner": "screen_english",
  "corner_label": "Screen English",
  "title": "",
  "movie": "갈매기 (The Seagull)",
  "duration_sec": 810.07,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2021-11-18_screen_english.mp3",
  "artwork_generated_url": "",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 4.08,
      "text": "사연 소개되신 두 분 모두 월간 굿모닝팝 3개월 구독권 보내드릴게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 4.9,
      "end": 9.3,
      "text": "굿모닝팝스에 사연 보내고 싶은 분들 공식 홈페이지 청취자 게시판에 남겨주세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 9.9,
      "end": 16.76,
      "text": "GMP로 영어실력 업, 에너지도 업, 열공 열일 하시다가 티타임 가지면서 여유를 즐겨보세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.76,
      "end": 19.64,
      "text": "따뜻한 카페라떼 쏴드립니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 20.34,
      "end": 24.68,
      "text": "신청해 주신 분들 중에 총 5분 뽑아서 모바일 쿠폰 보내드릴 텐데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 25.04,
      "end": 29.88,
      "text": "단문 50원과 장문 100원에 추가 요금이 부과되는 KBS 쿨 FM 문자샵 8910"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.88,
      "end": 37.26,
      "text": "아니면 KBS 이라디오 문자샵 1061로 신청하시거나 무료 KBS 어플리케이션 콩 또는 마이케이로 참여해 주세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 37.26,
      "end": 52.17,
      "text": "내일 아침 6시 조정현의 굿모닝팝"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.17,
      "end": 58.13,
      "text": "조정현의 굿모닝팝"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.13,
      "end": 63.18,
      "text": "조정현의 굿모닝팝"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.18,
      "end": 76.7,
      "text": "English"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.7,
      "end": 97.48,
      "text": "자막 없이 영화를 볼 수 있는 그날까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.48,
      "end": 99.08,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.08,
      "end": 101.58,
      "text": "11월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.58,
      "end": 102.78,
      "text": "아넷 반닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.78,
      "end": 104.3,
      "text": "서샤 로넌"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.3,
      "end": 106.46,
      "text": "빌리 하울 주연의"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.46,
      "end": 108.0,
      "text": "다시골 갈매기"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.0,
      "end": 108.75,
      "text": "워우"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.75,
      "end": 109.67,
      "text": "굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.67,
      "end": 110.67,
      "text": "헬로"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.67,
      "end": 112.41,
      "text": "top of the morning to you and everyone"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.41,
      "end": 113.11,
      "text": "GMP"
    },
    {
      "start": 113.11,
      "end": 114.11,
      "text": "굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.11,
      "end": 115.95,
      "text": "아니 제가 주중해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.95,
      "end": 116.79,
      "text": "during the week"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.79,
      "end": 118.47,
      "text": "되게 재미있었던 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.47,
      "end": 119.43,
      "text": "특히 혼자 있을 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.43,
      "end": 120.97,
      "text": "I've said the director's name"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.97,
      "end": 121.89,
      "text": "Anton Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.89,
      "end": 123.71,
      "text": "over and over again"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.71,
      "end": 124.89,
      "text": "You've said his name"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.89,
      "end": 127.07,
      "text": "이런 경험은 또 처음이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.07,
      "end": 127.83,
      "text": "Mr. Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.83,
      "end": 129.07,
      "text": "계속 생각이 나더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.07,
      "end": 130.97,
      "text": "He's an amazing playwright"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.97,
      "end": 132.61,
      "text": "legendary Russian playwright"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.61,
      "end": 133.57,
      "text": "그래서인가"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.57,
      "end": 134.81,
      "text": "Anton Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.81,
      "end": 135.85,
      "text": "Anton Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.85,
      "end": 138.37,
      "text": "이렇게 반복적으로 연습을 했던 기억이 납니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.37,
      "end": 139.25,
      "text": "It's a sexy name"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.25,
      "end": 140.57,
      "text": "그래서인가"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.57,
      "end": 141.01,
      "text": "Anton"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.01,
      "end": 141.57,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.57,
      "end": 144.33,
      "text": "And he was both a doctor and a writer"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.33,
      "end": 145.37,
      "text": "He was"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.37,
      "end": 146.01,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.01,
      "end": 146.33,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.33,
      "end": 148.83,
      "text": "He grew up from not a very wealthy family"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.83,
      "end": 150.15,
      "text": "His grandfather"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.15,
      "end": 151.49,
      "text": "paternal grandfather"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.49,
      "end": 152.61,
      "text": "Chinnareboji"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.61,
      "end": 153.87,
      "text": "was a serf"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.87,
      "end": 155.83,
      "text": "which is almost like a slave"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.83,
      "end": 156.89,
      "text": "back in Russia"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.89,
      "end": 158.55,
      "text": "similar to a slave"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.55,
      "end": 160.23,
      "text": "so from a very poor background"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.23,
      "end": 161.87,
      "text": "but he studied medicine"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.87,
      "end": 163.61,
      "text": "and he became a doctor"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.61,
      "end": 164.13,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.13,
      "end": 166.01,
      "text": "and also he loved writing"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.01,
      "end": 168.03,
      "text": "so he started writing short stories"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.03,
      "end": 169.69,
      "text": "and then plays"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.69,
      "end": 171.91,
      "text": "and he kept up his doctor life"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.91,
      "end": 173.09,
      "text": "to support his family"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.09,
      "end": 174.65,
      "text": "because he had a wife and kids"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.65,
      "end": 176.07,
      "text": "and he needed to pay the bills"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.07,
      "end": 177.89,
      "text": "so he kept on working"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.89,
      "end": 179.27,
      "text": "even though he got really sick"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.27,
      "end": 180.03,
      "text": "at one time"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.03,
      "end": 181.49,
      "text": "he caught tuberculosis"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.49,
      "end": 183.65,
      "text": "so he got deathly sick"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.65,
      "end": 185.03,
      "text": "but he just kept on working"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.03,
      "end": 186.69,
      "text": "and didn't even get it treated"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.69,
      "end": 191.55,
      "text": "굉장히 근면성실한 성격의 소유자였던 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.55,
      "end": 192.77,
      "text": "A hardworking man"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.77,
      "end": 194.55,
      "text": "And he succeeded eventually"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.55,
      "end": 195.81,
      "text": "as a playwright"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.81,
      "end": 196.89,
      "text": "너무 다행입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.89,
      "end": 199.91,
      "text": "And he also left many words"
    },
    {
      "start": 199.91,
      "end": 203.29,
      "text": "되게 흥미로운 어록들을 많이 남겼더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.29,
      "end": 205.87,
      "text": "And among them, this one was so funny"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.87,
      "end": 206.63,
      "text": "A funny one"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.63,
      "end": 207.81,
      "text": "Yeah, 제가 소개를 해드릴게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.81,
      "end": 211.43,
      "text": "If you are afraid of loneliness, don't marry"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.43,
      "end": 212.91,
      "text": "Don't marry?"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.97,
      "end": 214.17,
      "text": "Yeah, what do you think about this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.37,
      "end": 217.81,
      "text": "Well, let me speak carefully"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.81,
      "end": 218.99,
      "text": "Very carefully"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.99,
      "end": 220.65,
      "text": "네, 외로움이 두렵다면"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.65,
      "end": 222.03,
      "text": "결혼하지 마라"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.03,
      "end": 223.85,
      "text": "라는 어록을 남겼다고 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.85,
      "end": 226.79,
      "text": "If you are lonely, get married"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.79,
      "end": 228.37,
      "text": "이 얘기가 아니었단 말이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.37,
      "end": 231.09,
      "text": "Yeah, I would think that would be the thing to say"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.09,
      "end": 232.71,
      "text": "If you are alone, get married"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.71,
      "end": 235.69,
      "text": "But yeah, I've been a married man myself"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.69,
      "end": 238.63,
      "text": "with only females, women in the house"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.63,
      "end": 240.21,
      "text": "I do understand this"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.21,
      "end": 241.93,
      "text": "I do feel lonely sometimes"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.93,
      "end": 242.71,
      "text": "아, 그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.71,
      "end": 245.29,
      "text": "사실 we shouldn't rely too much on people"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.29,
      "end": 247.35,
      "text": "Yeah, you can't rely on people"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.35,
      "end": 247.73,
      "text": "그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.73,
      "end": 248.73,
      "text": "Even your own family"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.73,
      "end": 250.93,
      "text": "믿을 사람이 없는 건가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.65,
      "end": 253.13,
      "text": "아무튼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.13,
      "end": 254.87,
      "text": "But still, marriage is better than being alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.87,
      "end": 255.49,
      "text": "Yeah, sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.49,
      "end": 257.55,
      "text": "You'll be even more lonely in the end"
    },
    {
      "start": 257.55,
      "end": 258.37,
      "text": "if you just stay alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.37,
      "end": 259.51,
      "text": "In my opinion"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.51,
      "end": 261.09,
      "text": "So I support marriage"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.09,
      "end": 262.07,
      "text": "Get married"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.07,
      "end": 263.67,
      "text": "Do it like me"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.67,
      "end": 267.25,
      "text": "네, 결혼 장녀 이야기를 들으셨습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.25,
      "end": 268.95,
      "text": "다 똑같이 해야 돼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.95,
      "end": 270.33,
      "text": "전만 하면 안 돼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.33,
      "end": 271.53,
      "text": "다 같이"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.53,
      "end": 271.97,
      "text": "다 같이"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.97,
      "end": 272.37,
      "text": "하자"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.37,
      "end": 273.73,
      "text": "아, 오케이, 좋습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.73,
      "end": 275.59,
      "text": "오늘 장면 듣고 오겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.59,
      "end": 276.99,
      "text": "How do I begin?"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.25,
      "end": 278.03,
      "text": "Day and night"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.03,
      "end": 279.77,
      "text": "I am haunted"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.77,
      "end": 283.09,
      "text": "by a single obsessive thought"
    },
    {
      "start": 283.09,
      "end": 284.59,
      "text": "I must write"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.59,
      "end": 285.41,
      "text": "I must write"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.41,
      "end": 286.31,
      "text": "I must write"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.31,
      "end": 288.71,
      "text": "No sooner do I finish one story"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.71,
      "end": 290.71,
      "text": "than for God knows what reason"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.71,
      "end": 291.57,
      "text": "I have to write another"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.57,
      "end": 292.73,
      "text": "and another"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.73,
      "end": 293.41,
      "text": "and another"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.41,
      "end": 295.97,
      "text": "What's so beautiful and brilliant about that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.07,
      "end": 297.13,
      "text": "It's a ridiculous life"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.13,
      "end": 298.48,
      "text": "Here I am"
    },
    {
      "start": 298.48,
      "end": 299.8,
      "text": "I'm talking to you"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.8,
      "end": 301.62,
      "text": "I'm getting all riled up"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.72,
      "end": 303.47,
      "text": "네, 오늘은"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.47,
      "end": 306.59,
      "text": "Boris의 목소리를 쭉 들어보셨는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.59,
      "end": 308.73,
      "text": "Do you think he was happy enough?"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.73,
      "end": 310.37,
      "text": "He doesn't sound very happy"
    },
    {
      "start": 310.37,
      "end": 312.01,
      "text": "He seems kind of anxious"
    },
    {
      "start": 312.01,
      "end": 313.51,
      "text": "and nervous"
    },
    {
      "start": 313.51,
      "end": 315.55,
      "text": "He's really obsessed"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.55,
      "end": 317.41,
      "text": "He needs to write"
    },
    {
      "start": 317.41,
      "end": 318.43,
      "text": "He needs to write all the time"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.43,
      "end": 318.81,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.81,
      "end": 321.57,
      "text": "이제 막상 좋아하던 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 321.57,
      "end": 322.73,
      "text": "일이 되잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 322.73,
      "end": 323.07,
      "text": "그러면"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.07,
      "end": 325.73,
      "text": "마냥 행복하기만 한 것은 아니죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 325.73,
      "end": 326.21,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.21,
      "end": 327.73,
      "text": "If you watch him in the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.73,
      "end": 329.83,
      "text": "He's always looking at nature"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.83,
      "end": 329.85,
      "text": "He's always looking at nature"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.85,
      "end": 331.25,
      "text": "or looking around him"
    },
    {
      "start": 331.25,
      "end": 333.69,
      "text": "not just to enjoy the nature"
    },
    {
      "start": 333.69,
      "end": 334.93,
      "text": "but for his work"
    },
    {
      "start": 334.93,
      "end": 335.41,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.41,
      "end": 336.27,
      "text": "He takes notes"
    },
    {
      "start": 336.27,
      "end": 337.71,
      "text": "Oh, there's a cloud"
    },
    {
      "start": 337.71,
      "end": 338.95,
      "text": "It's a pretty cloud"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.95,
      "end": 340.39,
      "text": "I'm going to write about this cloud"
    },
    {
      "start": 340.39,
      "end": 342.29,
      "text": "So he has like"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.29,
      "end": 342.89,
      "text": "강박"
    },
    {
      "start": 342.89,
      "end": 344.15,
      "text": "강박이 진짜 심해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 344.15,
      "end": 344.87,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 344.87,
      "end": 346.07,
      "text": "저 같은 경우를"
    },
    {
      "start": 346.07,
      "end": 347.99,
      "text": "한번 감정이입을 해봤어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 347.99,
      "end": 348.87,
      "text": "저도 이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 348.87,
      "end": 350.39,
      "text": "영어를 좋아해가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 350.39,
      "end": 352.11,
      "text": "그래도 감사하게도"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.11,
      "end": 352.79,
      "text": "이 일을"
    },
    {
      "start": 352.79,
      "end": 353.91,
      "text": "직업을 삼아가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 353.91,
      "end": 354.95,
      "text": "살고 있지 않습니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 354.95,
      "end": 358.19,
      "text": "I just try to enjoy the pain"
    },
    {
      "start": 358.19,
      "end": 359.55,
      "text": "Enjoy the pain?"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.27,
      "end": 360.87,
      "text": "Ironically"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.87,
      "end": 362.59,
      "text": "That's an oxymoron"
    },
    {
      "start": 362.59,
      "end": 362.87,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 362.87,
      "end": 364.87,
      "text": "Sometimes it's really painful"
    },
    {
      "start": 364.87,
      "end": 366.51,
      "text": "and hard to stand"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.51,
      "end": 368.97,
      "text": "가끔은 저도 힘들 때가 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 368.97,
      "end": 369.37,
      "text": "Sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 369.37,
      "end": 370.13,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 370.13,
      "end": 371.77,
      "text": "There's a famous saying"
    },
    {
      "start": 371.77,
      "end": 373.05,
      "text": "No pain, no gain"
    },
    {
      "start": 373.05,
      "end": 373.51,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 373.51,
      "end": 376.39,
      "text": "That's the American Marine Corps saying"
    },
    {
      "start": 376.39,
      "end": 377.13,
      "text": "Yeah, 맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 377.13,
      "end": 378.11,
      "text": "미국 해병대"
    },
    {
      "start": 378.11,
      "end": 379.51,
      "text": "No pain, no gain"
    },
    {
      "start": 379.51,
      "end": 380.61,
      "text": "이라고 해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 380.61,
      "end": 381.23,
      "text": "맞습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 381.23,
      "end": 382.89,
      "text": "이 성취감을 위해서는"
    },
    {
      "start": 382.89,
      "end": 385.31,
      "text": "보통도 감내해야 하는 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 385.31,
      "end": 386.49,
      "text": "가끔 내려놓고"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.49,
      "end": 389.03,
      "text": "쉴 때가 제일 좋죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 389.03,
      "end": 390.79,
      "text": "저도 그럴게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.79,
      "end": 392.01,
      "text": "내려놓으세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 392.01,
      "end": 392.49,
      "text": "한 번씩"
    },
    {
      "start": 392.49,
      "end": 393.69,
      "text": "평상시에 좀 많이"
    },
    {
      "start": 393.69,
      "end": 394.97,
      "text": "쉬어보도록 하겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.97,
      "end": 396.63,
      "text": "오후에 혹은 저녁에"
    },
    {
      "start": 396.63,
      "end": 397.21,
      "text": "Ah, yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.21,
      "end": 397.91,
      "text": "Yeah, good idea"
    },
    {
      "start": 397.91,
      "end": 400.05,
      "text": "네, 표현들 점검해 볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 400.55,
      "end": 401.41,
      "text": "Haunted by"
    },
    {
      "start": 401.41,
      "end": 402.77,
      "text": "Haunted by"
    },
    {
      "start": 402.77,
      "end": 405.99,
      "text": "H-A-U-N-T-E-D"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.99,
      "end": 406.51,
      "text": "그 다음"
    },
    {
      "start": 406.51,
      "end": 407.05,
      "text": "By"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.05,
      "end": 407.89,
      "text": "B-Y"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.89,
      "end": 409.01,
      "text": "이렇게 들으셨어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.01,
      "end": 409.85,
      "text": "Haunted by"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.85,
      "end": 410.77,
      "text": "Ghosts"
    },
    {
      "start": 410.77,
      "end": 411.83,
      "text": "Spirits"
    },
    {
      "start": 411.83,
      "end": 412.09,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.09,
      "end": 412.91,
      "text": "주로 뒤에"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.91,
      "end": 413.71,
      "text": "Ghost 아니면"
    },
    {
      "start": 413.71,
